<h1>

<span class="mt-1 block section-head">
<span class="block text-black">Skin School: What is hyperpigmentation and how can you treat it?</span>
</span>
</h1>


<p class="mt-3 section-p text-gray-kk-text sm:mt-5">Dark spots, also known as hyperpigmentation, are caused by a number of different factors. How we treat it depends entirely on the root cause. Here’s everything you need to know about treating this very common condition…
</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 relative sm:max-w-lg sm:mx-auto lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:col-span-6 lg:flex lg:items-center">
