<div class="flex-1">
<p class="">
<a href="https://www.katekerrlondon.co.uk/skin-school-what-is-rosacea-and-how-can-you-treat-it/" class="section-head-alt text-gray-kk-text uppercase tag-text">
Skin School </a>
</p>
<a href="https://www.katekerrlondon.co.uk/skin-school-what-is-rosacea-and-how-can-you-treat-it/" class="block mt-2">
<p class="archive-post-title-skin-hq text-black">Skin School: What is rosacea and how can you treat it?</p>
<p class="mt-3 archive-post-excerpt-skin-hq text-gray-kk-text">When you have rosacea, controlling skin flare-ups and concealing redness can feel like a never-ending battle. It’s more common than you might think, with one...</p>
</a>
</div>
<div class="mt-6 flex items-center">
